{"tid":1739993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益] 外國文宣出路","createTime":"2019-11-19T21:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T02:22:41.000Z","uid":113051,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"814fdc5da154e8a918bcf39e2e970fbc6dd6b27b","tid":1739993,"uid":113051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:03:06.000Z","msg":"我知大家好注重外國文宣。依家的確好多外國人知道香港發生緊咩事，但好多外國人其實係睇完新聞、知道依事就算<br />\n一切都好難再進一步，因為就算人地想幫都唔知點幫好，以下係我係間外國大學reddit見到的一個post<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vDoEkPa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvDoEkPa.png&h=fd77e708&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3pXtYAR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3pXtYAR.png&h=aa07e2d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以一齊幫手諗下外國人可以點幫香港，之後係做外國文宣時張個方法推廣出去，令到外國文宣有大d的威力"},{"pid":"ca3260b256a1c6dc513d26bb2ac6f0d38d614a68","tid":1739993,"uid":113051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:11:16.000Z","msg":"其實之前nba果單野好好，但係果d機會可遇不可求<br />\n<br />\nnba已經幫我地鋪好咗條路，大家有冇得考慮下搞個#BoycottChina 之類的campaign，做到好似好耐之前果個ice bucket challenge，令d外國明星去就香港人權狀況去表態<br />\n<br />\n以上係拋磚引玉，歡迎大家公開討論"},{"pid":"0184fe3e8872e41c7fdc8623da63e6ba69b7bf9f","tid":1739993,"uid":113051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:20:13.000Z","msg":"大家見到覺得個idea okay就幫手推一下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7930968802bdd89025b1e9ffc5be50ed4d81eb9","tid":1739993,"uid":232101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:23:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f925aaf6dbd93f889348a3c5aec7b98b077aec9b","tid":1739993,"uid":113051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7930968802bdd89025b1e9ffc5be50ed4d81eb9","tid":1739993,"uid":232101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:23:32.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:35:02.000Z","msg":"感謝巴打，終於有人理我個依個小薯 <img src=\